UPHITSHIZWE yiloli ebelithwele isihlabathi abekotele kulo washona umfundi oneminyaka eyisithupha waseWaterloo, eVerulam, izolo. Lo mfana ofunda eDianthus Primary kuthiwa yena nabangani bakhe babonakale belenga kuleli loli ebelithwele isihlabathi ngesikhathi ewa epitshizeka. Kuthiwa leli iloli ebelithwele isihlabathi belilandelana nogandaganda, kuyiwa lapho bekuyosetshenzwa khona. Ngesikhathi lezi zimoto zilandelana kuPineapple Street, lo mfana nabangani bakhe kuthiwa bakotele kulezi zimoto balenga kuzo. UMnuz Prem Balram, we-Reaction Unit South Africa (Rusa), uthe ngokuthola kwabo umfana oshonile uwe kwenye yalezi zimoto wapitshizeka washona. Uthe abakwaRusa bafonelwe amalungu omphakathi akule ndawo ethi abaphuthume kunomfana odinga usizo lwezempilo ngokushesha. “Siphuthume kule ndawo safica umfana elele ngaphansi kweloli ebelinesihlabathi esingamamitha ayisithupha. Umfana kutholakale ukuthi useshonile khona endaweni yesigameko. Ubelimele kanzima ekhanda. Ngokuthola kwethu lo mfana nabangani bakhe bebelenga elolini yena wawa, wawela emgwaqweni, wapitshizwa yiloli,” kusho yena. Okhulumela amaphoyisa KwaZulu-Natal, uCol Thembeka Mbele, uthe amaphoyisa aseVerulam avule icala lokubulala ngokungenhloso kulandela ukuthi umfana oneminyaka eyisithupha epitshizwe yiloli eWaterloo.   